error_message: LangchainLLMCalculator - The following expression Thomas withdraws $10000 in 20 dollar bills from the bank account. He loses 100 bills while getting home. After that, he uses half of the remaining bills to pay for a bill. Thomas then triples his money. He then converts all his bills to 10 dollar bills. How many 5 dollar bills does he have? is not expected to return a single numerical value
